[[File:Diamond-and-graphite.jpg]]

'''Kaarboon''' ([[Ingiriis]]: Carbon «Element») calaamad [[C]]  waa [[curiye]] kimiko ah oo [[tiro]]da [[atom]]kiisu tahay [[lix]]. 
Kaarboonku waa curiyeha ugu caansan dhamaan [[Diwaanka Curiye]] kaas oo [[Adem]]uhu yaqaaneen ilaa [[wakhti]] hore. 

Sida dabeeciga ah, [[Curiye]]han waxa laga heelaa oogada [[dhul]]ka asagoo [[sadex]] isotope ah, sida 12C iyo 13C oo ah kuwo dhismahoodu miisaamah yahay, iyo 14C oo ah ''radioactive''. 

Kaarboonku markuu la [[mataan]]oowo [[curiye]] kale waxaa soo baxa [[macdan]] aad u qaali ah, sida [[dheeman]]ta, graphite-ka iyo amorphous.

